 times now. Always great service and pricing! Would definitely recommend especially after using other junk removal companies previously before finding junk king -and they would always charge extra fees etc. They cleaned up, no debris or nails and screws. Prices are good. Thanks Junk or Haul<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><div class='avia-testimonial-meta'><div class='avia-testimonial-arrow-wrap'><div class='avia-arrow'><\/div><\/div><div class='avia-testimonial-image'  itemprop=\"image\"  style='background-image:url(https:\/\/junkorhaul.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/1-180x180.png);'><\/div><div class='avia-testimonial-meta-mini'  itemprop=\"author\" itemscope=\"itemscope\" itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Person\" ><strong  class='avia-testimonial-name'   style='color:#32cd32; '  itemprop=\"name\" >D. Mika<\/strong><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<div class='avia-testimonial av_one_full flex_column no_margin avia-testimonial-row-1 ' ><div class='avia-testimonial_inner'  itemscope=\"itemscope\" itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/CreativeWork\" ><div class='avia-testimonial-content av_inherit_color'  style='color:#ffffff; ' ><div class='avia-testimonial-markup-entry-content'  itemprop=\"text\" ><p>\u2b50\u2b50\u2b50\u2b50<\/p>\n<p>These guys were great. I highly recommend the service if you would like to remove junk from your house. They were quick and efficient. Also they were thorough which was wonderful because it made my job easier closing the apartment out of the end. Thank you very much gentlemen. I will not only recommend the service to others when possible, I will also proactively suggest the service. Thank you Junk or Haul.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><div class='avia-testimonial-meta'><div class='avia-testimonial-arrow-wrap'><div class='avia-arrow'><\/div><\/div><div class='avia-testimonial-image'  itemprop=\"image\"  style='background-image:url(https:\/\/junkorhaul.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/10-180x180.png);'><\/div><div class='avia-testimonial-meta-mini'  itemprop