imonial-content av_inherit_color'  style='color:#ffffff; ' ><div class='avia-testimonial-markup-entry-content'  itemprop=\"text\" ><p>\u2b50\u2b50\u2b50\u2b50\u2b50<\/p>\n<p>Appointment was easy to do; the guys came by gave me a fair price and took the item away. Easy ! Second time used the service and has always been courteous and easy to work with.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><div class='avia-testimonial-meta'><div class='avia-testimonial-arrow-wrap'><div class='avia-arrow'><\/div><\/div><div class='avia-testimonial-image'  itemprop=\"image\"  style='background-image:url(https:\/\/junkorhaul.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/8-180x180.png);'><\/div><div class='avia-testimonial-meta-mini'  itemprop=\"author\" itemscope=\"itemscope\" itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Person\" ><strong  class='avia-testimonial-name'   style='color:#32cd32; '  itemprop=\"name\" >Mandy Casten<\/strong><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<div class='avia-testimonial av_one_full flex_column no_margin avia-testimonial-row-1 ' ><div class='avia-testimonial_inner'  itemscope=\"itemscope\" itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/CreativeWork\" ><div class='avia-testimonial-content av_inherit_color'  style='color:#ffffff; ' ><div class='avia-testimonial-markup-entry-content'  itemprop=\"text\" ><p>\u2b50\u2b50\u2b50\u2b50\u2b50<\/p>\n<p>The guys were very friendly and helpful. They called before arrival which was very helpful. I will use Junk or Haul for sure in the future.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><div class='avia-testimonial-meta'><div class='avia-testimonial-arrow-wrap'><div class='avia-arrow'><\/div><\/div><div class='avia-testimonial-image'  itemprop=\"image\"  style='background-image:url(https:\/\/junkorhaul.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/3-180x180.png);'><\/div><div class='avia-testimonial-meta-mini'  itemprop=\"author\" itemscope=\"itemscope\" itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Person\" ><strong  class='avia-testimonial-name'   style='color:#32cd32; '  itemprop=\"name\" >John Chang<\/strong><\/div><\/div><